===Noun===
'''Sinn'''

# [[sense]], [[meaning]]
# [[point]], [[idea]], [[tenor]]
# [[mind]], [[consciousness]]
# [[feeling]]
# (''med'') [[sense]], [[sensus]], [[aesthesia]] (''Brit'')/[[esthesia]] (''Am'')

